hadiths[70]{hadithnumber,text}:
3571,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney qazi ka ohda liya to wo chhuri ke baghair hi zibeh kar diya gaya.''"
3572,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya: ''jisey logon ka qazi bana diya gaya usey chhuri ke baghair hi zibeh kar diya gaya.''"
3573,"Janab ( Abdullah (bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qazi teen tarah ke hotey hain : eik jannat mein hai aur do aag mein. jannat mein janey wala wo hai jisney haq pehchaana aur uskey mutabiq faisla kiya, aur jisney haq pehchaana aur phir faisley mein zulm kiya to wo aag mein hai, aur jisney jahil hotey huey logon ke faisley kiye wo bhi aag mein hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is mauzu mein ye hadees sahih tareen hai. yani ibne Barida ki hadees ke qazi teen tarah ke hotey hain."
3574,"Hazrat Amr bin Al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''jab koi haakim faisla karey aur khoob soch bichaar aur ijtihaad se kaam ley aur durust natijey par pahunchey to uskey liye do guna ajr hai, aur jab koi khoob soch bichaar aur ijtihaad se kaam ley aur us se khata ho jaey to uskey liye eik ajr hai.'' (Yazid bin Abdullah bin Haad ne kaha) maine ye riwayat Abu-Bakar bin Hazam ko bayan ki to unhoney kaha : mujhey Abu-Salma ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se aisey hi riwayat ki hai."
3575,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney musalmanon mein qaza ka mansab (pad) talab kiya yahan tak ke usey hasil kar liya, phir uska adl karna zulm kerney par ghalib raha , to uskey liye jannat hai, aur jis ka zulm uskey adl par ghalib raha, uskey liye jahannam hai.''"
3576,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Sura Maayda ki ye teeno aayaat (وَمَنْ لَمْ يَحْكُمْ بِمَا أَنْزَلَ اللَّهُ فَأُولَئِكَ هُمْ الْكَافِرُونَ . . . الْفَاسِقُونَ) yahudiyon ke qabaayel bil-khusus Qureza aur bano Nazeer ke mutalliq nazil hui thin.
3577,Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Bishr Ansari Al Azraq kehtey hain (ke ghaaliban koofa mein) baabe kinda ki taraf se do aadmi aaye jabkey Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) halqey mein tashrif farma they. un dono ne kaha : kya koi ham mein faisla nahin kar deta? halqey mein se eik aadmi ne kaha : main kar deta hun. to Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kankariyon ki mutthi bhari aur usey dey maari aur farmaya : baaz raho. faisla kerney mein jald bazi napasand samjhi jati thi. (yani Sahaba kiram mein.)
3578,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''jisney qazi ka ohda talab kiya aur uskey liye logon se madad chahi (sifaarishein karaaein) to ye mansab (pad) aur kaam usi par dal diya jaeyga. (Allah ki taraf se uski koi madad na hogi) aur jisney usey talab kiya na logon se madad chahi, tu Allah taala eik farishta nazil farmata hai jo usey sidhi raah sujhaata rehta hai. Wakee ne is riwayat ki sanad yun bayan ki hai : ( عن  إسرائيل  ،  عن عبد الأعلى  ، عن بلال بن أبي موسى  ،  عن أنس  ، an النبي ﷺ) aur Abu-Awaana ne kaha (عن عبد الأعلى  ،  عن بلال بن مرداس الفزاري  ،  عن خيثمة البصري  ،  عن أنس)."
3579,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi is mansab (pad) aur kaam ka talabgar hoga ham usey hergiz nahin dengey.''"
3580,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rishwat deney waley aur leney waley ko lanat farmaee hai.
3581,"Hazrat Adi bin Umaira Kandi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logo ! tum mein se jis kisi ko hamari taraf se koi amaldaari sonpi gaee ho, phir usney uskey mahaasil mein se koi sooi ya is se bhi kam ya ziyada ko chhupa liya, to wo tauq hai jisey pehney huey wo qiyamat ke roz hazir hoga.'' to kalay se rang ka , eik Ansari jawan khada ho gaya , goya main usey dekh raha hun. kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujh se apna kaam wapis ley lijiye. aapney puchha : ''kya hua ?'' usney kaha : maine aap ko suna hai ke aap yun yun farma rahey hain. aapney farmaya : ''(haan) mein yehi kehta hun. jis ko ham ne koi kaam saunpa ho to usey chahiye ke uskey mahaasil, thodey hon ya ziyada , sab ley aaye. aur phir us mein se jo usey (khidmat ka haq) diya jaey wo le-ley aur jis se rok diya jaey us se ruk jaey.''"
3582,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey Yamen ka qazi bana kar rawana farmaya to maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main nau-umr hun aur mujhey faisla kerney ka ilm nahin hai. aapney farmaya : ''yaqeenan Allah taala tumharey dil ko hidayat dega aur tumhari zaban ko Sabit rakhega. jab muqaddmey ke do fareeq tumharey samney baithein to us waqt tak hergiz faisla na karna jab tak doosrey se sun na lena jaisey ke pehley se suna ho. bila-shuba yehi chiz ziyada layaq hai ke faisla tumharey liye wazeh ho jaey.''  Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : chunanche main wahan qazi bana raha ya (farmaya) mujhey uskey baad faisla kerney mein koi taraddud (sankoch) nahin hua.
3583,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main eik Bashr (insan) hun, tum apney jhagdey merey paas latey ho aur ho sakta hai ke tum mein se koi doosrey ke muqabley main apni hujjat pesh kerney mein ziyada tez-zaban ho aur phir main us se sunney ke mutabiq faisla kar dun, to jis ke liye main uskey bhai ke haq ka faisla kar dun to wo us se kuchh na ley. bila-shuba mein uskey liye aag ka tukda kaat raha hun.''"
3584,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas do aadmi aaye unka meeras ke maamley mein jhagda tha aur unke paas siwaye apney apney daway ke aur koi gawah na tha. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : aur mazkura baala hadees ki misl bayan kiya. chunanche wo dono roney lagey aur her eik doosrey se kehney laga : mera haq terey liye hai. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un dono se farmaya : ''jab tum aisa kartey ho to aapas mein taqseem kar lo aur haq ka irada karo phir aapas mein quraa dal lo (hissey ko chun'ne ke liye) phir mumkina ziyadti eik doosrey se maaf kara lo.''
3585,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees bayan ki. un do aadmiyon ka virasat mein jhagda tha aur bhi chand dusri chizen thin jinkey nishaanaat mit gaey they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis cheez mein mujh par kuchh nazil na hua ho us mein , main apni raey se faisla karta hun.''"
3586,Ibne-Shahab Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne riwayat kiya ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne member par chadh kar farmaya : aey logo ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki raey bilkul bar-haq hua karti thi kyonkey unhen Allah taala sujhaata tha aur hamari raey khayal aur guman hoti hai.
3587,Ahmed bin Abda Zabbi kehtey hain ke hamein Muaz bin Muaz ne bayan kiya. kaha ke mujhey Abu-Usman Shami (Hareez bin Usman) ne bayan kiya aur) Muaz bin Muaz ne kaha ke) main kisi Shami ko Hareez bin Usman se afzal nahin samajhta.
3588,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya hai ke muddai aur jis par daawa kiya gaya ho dono qazi ke samney baithen.
3589,Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakra apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney apney sahibzadey ki taraf likh bheja ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi hukm (faisla kerney wala) ghussay ki haalat mein dono fariqon mein faisla na karey.''
3590,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke pehley ye aayat nazil hui (فَإِنْ جَاءُوكَ فَاحْكُمْ بَيْنَهُمْ أَوْ أَعْرِضْ عَنْهُمْ) ''agar ye (yahood) aap ke paas ayen to aap un mein faisla farmaeyn ya aeraz kar lein (rehne den).'' phir usey mansookh kar diya gaya aur farmaya : (فَاحْكُمْ بَيْنَهُمْ بِمَا أَنْزَلَ اللَّهُ) ''aap un mein faisla farmaeyn us chiz ke sath jo Allah ne nazil ki.''
3591,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke jab ye aayat kareema (فَإِنْ جَاءُوكَ فَاحْكُمْ بَيْنَهُمْ أَوْ أَعْرِضْ عَنْهُمْ وَإِنْ تُعْرِضْ عَنْهُمْ فَلَنْ يَضُرُّوكَ شَيْئًا وَإِنْ حَكَمْتَ فَاحْكُمْ بَيْنَهُمْ بِالْقِسْطِ إِنَّ اللَّهَ يُحِبُّ الْمُقْسِطِينَ) nazil hui, (unhoney sabab (wajah) nuzool) bayan kiya ke bano Nazeer, banu Qureza ke kisi shakhs ko qatl kar detey to aadhi diyat diya kartey aur agar bano Qureza, bano Nazeer ka koi aadmi qatl kar detey to puri diyat detey they. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey un mein barabar barabar kar diya."
3592,Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ke baaz as-haab (sathiyon) ne riwayat kiya jo ehale-hims mein se they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab irada farmaya ke Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen bhejen to aapney puchha : ''jab koi muqadma tumharey samney pesh hoga to faisla kaisey karogey?'' unhoney kaha : main Allah ki kitab se faisla karunga. aapney farmaya : ''agar kitabe-Allah mein na mila to? ''kaha ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat se. farmaya : ''agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat aur kitabe-Allah mein bhi na mila to? ''kaha ke main apni raey istimal kerney mein kami nahin karunga. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unka seena thapkaaya aur farmaya : ''hamd hai us Allah ki jisney Rasulullah ke payaambar ko is baat ki taufiq di jis par Allah ka Rasool khush hai.''
3593,Muaz ke kuchh sathiyon ne Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen jab Yamen bheja . aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
3594,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''musalmanon ka aapas mein suleh kar lena jayez hai (yani ye nafiz (laagu) hogi). Ahmed (bin Abdul-Waahid) ne mazeed kaha : ''siwaye aisi suleh ke jo kisi haram ko halal ya kisi halal ko haram banaey. Sulaiman bin Dawud ne izafa kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''musalman apni sharton ke paband hain.''
3595,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein aapney ibne-Abi Hadrad se apney qarzey ka mutalba kiya. ye masjid mein they ke unki aawazen oonchi ho gaeen jinhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney ghar mein suna. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki taraf nikley aur apney hujrey ka parda uthaya aur Kab bin Malik ko aawaz detey huey kaha : ''aey Kab !'' usney kaha : main hazir hun, aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney apney haath se usey ishara farmaya ke apna aadha qarza chhod do. Kab ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine maaf kiya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne doosrey se farmaya : ''uth aur usey ada kar dey.''"
3596,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen behtareen gawah na bataun? wo jo talab kerney se pehley khud se apni gawahi pesh kar dey.'' Abdullah bin Ubai Bakr ko alfaze-hadees mein shak hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : us se murad ye hai ke sahibe-haq ko ilm na ho ke uska gawah kon hai? Hamdaani ne kaha : wo (khud se) apney aap ko sultan ke rubaru pesh kar dey. Ibne Sarah ne kaha : ya Imam (haakim) ke samney pesh kar dey. Hamdaani ki riwayat mein (أخبرنا) hai. Ibne Sarah ne (raawi ka naam) ibne-Abi Umra zikr kiya hai, Abdur-Rehman (bin Abi Umra) nahin zikr kiya."
3597,"Yahya bin Rashid ne bayan kiya ke ham Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke intizar mein baithey they yahan tak ke wo tashrif ley aaye aur baithey phir kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''jis shakhs ki sifarish Allah ki kisi had ki tanfeez (laagu karne) mein aadey aai, tehqiq usney Allah ki mukhalifat ki aur jisney jantey boojhtey batil (ki himayat) mein jhagda kiya to wo Allah ki narazi mein rahega yahan tak ke us se baaz aa jaey aur jisney kisi momin ke baarey mein koi aisi baat kahi jo us mein nahin thi tu Allah usey jahannamiyon ki peep mein daley ga (wo usi ka mustahiq rahega) yahan tak ke apni baat se baaz aa jaey.''"
3598,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya. farmaya : ''jisney kisi zulm ke jhagdey mein muaawinat (madad) ki tehqiq wo Shan Wale Allah ki narazi ke sath lauta.''
3599,"Hazrat Khuraim bin Faatik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fajr ki Namaz padhaai. jab us se farigh huey to sidhey khadey ho gaey aur farmaya : ''jhooti gawahi dena , Allah ke sath shareek thehraney ke barabar hai. teen baar farmaya. phir aapney ye aayat tilawat farmaai :(فَاجْتَنِبُوا الرِّجْسَ مِنَ الْأَوْثَانِ وَاجْتَنِبُوا قَوْلَ الزُّورِ حُنَفَاءَ لِلَّهِ غَيْرَ مُشْرِكِينَ بِهِ) ''buton ki paleedi (gandagi) se bacho aur jhooti baat se ijtinab (bacha) karo, Allah ki taraf yaksoo raho is haal mein ke uskey sath shirk kerney waley na ho.''"
3600,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo (Shoaib) apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaain (khayanat karne wale) mard , khaain aurat aur apney bhai ke sath keena aur bughz rakhney waley ki gawahi radd farmaai hai. aur aisey hi jo kisi ghar walon ka khidmat gaar (naukar, ghulam aur tabey) ho, uski gawahi bhi qubul nahin ki. albatta doosron ke haq mein qubul hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain (الغمر) ka maani bughz aur adawat hai. aur (القانع) se murad tabey rehney wala hai jaisey ke koi khas naukar hota hai."
3601,"Sulaiman bin Musa ne apni sanad se bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''kisi khaain (khayanat karne wale) mard ya aurat , zaani mard ya aurat ya apney bhai ke baarey mein bughz aur adawat rakhney waley ki gawahi jayez nahin.''"
3602,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''ke kisi dehati ki shahri ke khilaf gawahi jayez nahin.''"
3603,Janab ibne-Abi Mulaika kehtey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Aqba bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya. aur mujhey ye riwayat merey eik aur sathi ne bhi Aqba se bayan ki aur apney sathi ki riwayat mujhey ziyada yaad hai. kaha ke maine Umme- Yahya binte-Abi Ihaab se shaadi ki. to hamarey paas eik kaali aurat aai aur usney kaha ke maine un dono ko doodh pilaya hai. to main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se ye waqia bayan kiya. to aapney mujh se munh pher liya. maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! beshak wo jhooti hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tujhey kya khabar? halanke usney jo kehna tha keh diya hai. us aurat (apni biwi) ko chhod dey.''
3604,Ibne-Abi Mulaika ne ba-waaste Ubaid bin Abi Maryam Hazrat Aqba bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya. ibne-Abi Mulaika ne kaha ke maine ye riwayat Hazrat Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi suni hai magar mujhey Ubaid ka bayan ziyada zabt hai. aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hammad bin Zaid ne Haris bin Umair ko dekha aur kaha : ye Ayub ke motamid (bharosemand) shagirdon mein se hai.
3605,"Janab Shobi (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke eik musalman ki daquqaa maqam par wafat ho gaee. usey koi musalman na mila jo uski wasiyat par gawah hota. to usney ehle-kitab ke do aadmiyon ko gawah banaya. phir wo dono koofa mein Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye aur unko uski khabar di aur uska tarka aur wasiyat bhi pesh ki. Hazrat Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye maamla Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur ke baad nahin hua hai. to unhoney Asr ke baad un se Allah ke naam ki qasam li ke unhoney kisi qism ki khayanat , jhoot ya tabdeeli nahin ki hai, kuchh chupaya hai na koi badlaw kiya hai, aur us maiyat ki wasiyat aur tarka yehi kuchh hai. chunanche unhoney unki gawahi ko qubul kar liya."
3606,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke bano saham ka eik shakhs Tameem daari aur Adi bin Baddaa ke sath main safar par nikla. (daurane-safar) Sehmi ki wafat ho gaee jahan ke koi musalman na tha. jab wo dono uska tarka lekar aaye to (warison ne) chaandi ka eik piyala gum paya jis par soney ke patrey chadhey huey they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un dono se qasam li. phir baad mein wo jaam Makka mein mil gaya. (jinkey paas se mila) unhoney kaha ke ham ne ye Tameem aur Adi se kharida hai. phir marney waley Sehmi ke warison mein se do ne qasam khai aur kaha ke hamari gawahi unki gawahi se ziyada sachchi hai aur ye jaam hamarey aadmi ka hai. chunanche unhi ke silsiley mein ye aayat nazil hui (يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا شَهَادَةُ بَيْنِكُمْ إِذَا حَضَرَ أَحَدَكُمُ الْمَوْتُ)."
3607,"Janab Umara bin Khuzaima se riwayat hai ke unke chacha ne bayan kiya jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik badwi se ghoda kharida. aur badwi se kaha ke merey sath aao taake tumharey ghodey ki qeemat ada kar dun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jaldi jaldi chaley jabkey Erab (dehati) aahista aahista chala. to log us badwi ke samney aaye aur ghodey ka soda kerney lagey. unhen ilm nahin tha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey kharid liya hai. to us badwi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pukara aur kaha : agar ghoda khareednaa hai to kharid lo warna mein isey farokht kar dunga. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski aawaz sun kar ruk gaey aur farmaya : ''kya maine usey tum se kharid nahin liya?'' badwi ne kaha : nahin qasam Allah ki ! maine to isey tum ko nahin bechaa. aapney farmaya : ''kyon nahin, maine tum se kharida liya hai.'' badwi kehney laga chalo gawah lao. to Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) boley : main gawahi deta hun ke to ne ye bech diya hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Khuzaima ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''tum kis tarah gawahi detey ho?'' unhoney arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap ki tasdeeq ki bina par (yani aap Allah ke Rasool hain jhoot nahin bol saktey aur aap hamein wo kuchh batatey hain jo ham nahi dekhten lekin uskey bawajood ham wo sab kuchh tasleem kartey hain to ye kyon nahin tasleem kar saktey.) chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Khuzaima (Raziallahu anhu) ki gawahi ko do aadmiyon ki gawahi ke barabar qarar dey diya."
3608,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik gawah ke sath qasam lekar faisla farmaya. (muddai se qasam li .)
3609,"Janab Amr bin Dinar (Rahimahullah) ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. Salma (bin Shabeeb) ki riwayat mein hai, Amr ne kaha ke ''(maali) huqooq mein'' (is tarah se faisla kiya.)"
3610,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik gawah ke sath qasam lekar faisla farmaya. (yani muddai se qasam li.) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Rabeea bin Sulaiman Muazzin ne mujhey is riwayat mein mazeed kaha ke hamein Imam Shafai (Rahimahullah) ne Abdul-Azeez se riwayat kiya. Abdul-Azeez ne kaha ke maine Suhel bin Abi Saleh se ye hadees poochhi to kaha ke mujhey (merey shagrid) Rabeea Raaee ne bayan kiya aur wo merey nazdik motamid (bharosemand) hai, kaha ke main (Suhail) hi ne Rabeea ko ye hadees bayan ki thi. jo mujhey yaad nahin. Abdul-Azeez kehtey hain ke Janab Suhel bimar ho gaey they. jis se unki yaaddaasht zaayel (khatm) ho gaee aur unhen apni kaee hadisein yaad nahi rahi. chunanche Suhel uskey baad yun sanad bayan kya kartey they ke mujhey Rabeea ne mujh se riwayat kiya ke mujhey merey walid ne bayan kiya."
3611,"Sulaiman bin Bilal ne Rabeea se Abu Musab Zohri ki mazkura baala sanad se usi ke ham-maani riwayat kiya, Sulaiman ne kaha ke main Suhel se mila aur un se ye hadees daryaft ki to unhoney kaha : mujhey maloom nahin. maine kaha ke mujhey Rabeea ne aap ke wastey se riwayat ki hai. to unhoney kaha : agar Rabeea ne tumhen bataya hai ke usney mujh se riwayat kiya hai to usey ba-waaste Rabeea mujh se riwayat karo."
3612,"Hazrat Zubaib bin Solba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna eik lashkar banu-anbar ki taraf rawana kiya. unhoney taaif ke muzaafat mein rukba maqam par us qabiley ko ja pakda aur unhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf ley aaye. main sawar hua aur un se pehley Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunch gaya. maine kaha : ''aey Allah ke Nabi ! aap par salamti ho aur aap par Allah ki rahmatein aur barkaten nazil hon. aap ka lashkar hamarey yahan pahuncha aur usney hamen pakad liya halanke ham ne (pehley hi) Islam qubul kar liya tha aur apney janwaron ke kaan bhi kaat daley they. jab bano anbar ke log pahunch gaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : ''kya tumharey paas koi gawah hai ke tum pakdey janey se pehley un dinon (dinon) mein musalman ho chukey they?'' maine kaha : haan. aapney farmaya : '' terey gawah kon hain?'' maine arz kiya ke bano anbar ka eik fard Samura aur eik doosrey aadmi ka naam liya. chunanche us doosrey ne shahadat di lekin Samura ne shahadat deney se inkar kiya. isliye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usney gawahi deney se inkar kiya hai, lihaza tujhey apney doosrey gawah ke sath qasam uthani hogi.'' maine kaha : haan (uthaaunga) to aapney mujh se qasam li aur maine kaha ke Allah ki qasam ! ham log falan falan roz Islam qubul kar chukey they aur apney janwaron ke kaan kaat chukey they. (ye Islam aur adame-Islam ke darmiyan farq kerney ka eik andaz tha.) tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (apney mujahideen sey) farmaya : '' jao aur in se nisf-nisf (aadha-aadha) maal ley lo aur inki auladon ko haath mat lagao. (unhen ghulam mat banao) agar ye baat na hoti ke Allah taala kisi ke amal (aur uski mehnat) ko zaya nahin farmata hai to ham tum se eik rassi bhi na letey.'' Zubaib ne kaha : phir mujhey meri walida ne bulaya aur bataya ke us aadmi ne mujh se meri to-shak li hai. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas gaya yani aap ko khabar di to aapney mujhey farmaya : ''usey roko.'' to maine usko gireban se pakad liya aur apni jagah par uskey sath ruka raha. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khadey dekha to farmaya : ''tu apney qaidi ke sath kya karna chahta hai?'' to maine usko chhod diya. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey aur us aadmi se farmaya : ''uski maa ki toshak jo to ne us se li hai usko wapis kar do.'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! wo mujh se zaya ho gaee hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski talwaar utaari aur mujhey de-di aur usey farmaya : ''jao aur ghalley ke chand saa aur mazeed bhi do.'' chunanche usney mujhey kaee saa jau bhi de diye."
3613,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aadmiyon ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke huzur eik oont ya kisi janwar ka daawa kiya lekin kisi ke paas gawah nahin tha, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey un dono ke beech (aadha-aadha) kar diya."
3614,Janab Saeed (bin Abi Burda (Rahimahullah) ( ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
3615,Janab Qatada (Rahimahullah) ne apni sanad se bayan kiya jo mazkura baala hadees ke qarib-qarib hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein do aadmiyon ne eik oont ka daawa kiya aur un dono ne do do gawah bhi pesh kar diye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey unke beech nisf-nisf (aadha-aadha) kar diya.
3616,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aadmi kisi maal ka tanaaza' (jhagdaa) lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye. un mein se kisi ke paas gawah nahin tha. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasam khaney ke liye qura dal lo, jis ka bhi nikal aaye, tumhen ye pasand ho ya na.'' (is ka yehi hal hai ke jo qasam khaye ga maal le-ley ga.)"
3617,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''agar dono qasam khana napasand keren ya dono hi qasam khana chahen to qasam khaney ke liye qura dal lein. Salma (bin Shabeeb) ne kaha : hamein Maamer ne khabar di ke jab dono qasam khaney par majboor kar diye jaeyn to qura dal lein (ke kon qasam khaye).
3618,"Janab Saeed bin Abi Aruba ne Hajjaj bin Minhaal ki sanad se is hadees ke misl (jaisi) riwayat kiya, kaha ke do aadmiyon ne eik janwar ke silsile mein jhagda kiya aur kisi ke paas gawah nahin tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen hukm diya ke qasam khaney ke liye qura dalen."
3619,Ibne-Abi Mulaika se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne mujhey likh bheja ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya tha ke (jab muddai ke paas gawah na hon to) jis daawa kiya jae wo qasam khaye.
3620,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us aadmi se farmaya jis ko aapney qasam uthwaai ke : ''tu Allah ki qasam kha jiskey siwa koi mabud nahin, ke terey paas is muddai ki koi cheez nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya ke raawi Abu-Yahya ka naam Ziyad hai jo koofi hai aur bharosemand hai."
3621,"Hazrat Ash'as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehtey hain ke merey aur eik yahudi ke beech zameen ki sharaakat daari thi , jo wo mujhey deney se inkari ho gaya. to main usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''kya koi tumhara gawah hai? ''maine kaha : nahin. aapney yahudi se kaha : ''qasam uthao.'' maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo to qasam utha lega aur mera maal maar lega, tu Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farma di (إِنَّ الَّذِينَ يَشْتَرُونَ . .) ''beshak jo log Allah ke ehad aur apni qasmon ko thodi qeemat par bech daltey hain unke liye aakhirat mein koi hissey nahin, Allah taala un se na to baat kerega aur na qiyamat ke din unki taraf dekhega , na unhen paak kerega aur un ke liye dard naak azab hai.''"
3622,"Hazrat Ash'as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke bano kinda aur hazare-maut ke do aadmi apni eik zameen ka tanaaza' (jhagda) lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye , wo zameen Yamen mein thi. Hizrami ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! iskey walid ne meri zameen ghasab karli thi aur wo ab iskey qabzey mein hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us (Hizrami) se puchha : ''kya tera koi gawah hai?'' usney kaha : nahin. lekin main usey (Kindi ko) Allah ki qasam de-kar poochhta hun kya ye nahin janta ke ye meri zameen hai aur uskey baap ne mujh se ghasab kar rakhi thi? chunanche wo Kindi qasam khaney ke liye tayyar ho gaya. aur (ibne Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( aagey hadees bayan ki. (dekhiye, hadees : 3244)"
3623,"Hazrat Alqama bin Waael bin Hajar Hizrami apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke hazare-maut aur bano kinda ke do aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye . Hizrami ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye aadmi meri zameen par qaabiz ho gaya hai jo ke merey walid ki thi. Kindi ne kaha : ye zameen meri hai, merey qabzey mein hai, main hi usey kaasht kar raha hun, iska us mein koi haq nahin hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hizrami se kaha : ''kya tera koi gawah hai? '' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''to phir terey liye uski qasam hai.'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye faajir (badkar) aadmi hai, isey koi parwa nahin ke kya qasam kha raha hai. isey kisi cheez ka perhez aur dar nahin hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' terey liye is se bas yehi hai.''"
3624,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yahudiyon se kaha : ''main tumhen us Allah ki qasam deta hun jisney Musa Alehissalam par Taurat nazil farmaee, tum log zaani ke baarey mein Taurat mein kya paatey ho?'' aur qissa rajm (sangsaar) ke baarey mein hadees bayan ki."
3625,"Janab Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne apni sanad se ye hadees bayan ki, kaha ke mujhey muzena qabiley ke eik aadmi ne bayan kiya jo sahibe-ilm aur haafiz tha, usney Saeed bin Musaiyab se riwayat kiya aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya."
3626,"Janab Ikrima (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ibne Sureeya (yahudi) se kaha : ''main tumhen us Allah ki yaad dilata hun jisney tumhen aale Firon se najat di, tumharey liye samandar ko shaqq kiya, tum par badalon ka saya kiya aur man aur salwaa nazil kiya aur tumharey liye Hazrat Musa Alehissalam par Taurat nazil farmaey, kya tum apni kitab mein rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm paatey ho?'' usney kaha : aapney mujhey badi azeem zaat ki yaad dilai hai aur merey liye mumkin nahin ke aap ko jhutla sakoon . aur hadees bayan ki."
3627,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do aadmiyon mein faisla kiya. to muqadma haar janey waley ne peeth pheri aur kaha : (حسبي الله ونعم الوكيل) ''mujhey Allah kafi hai aur wo behtareen karsaz hai.'' to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala aajizi (aur mehnat aur koshish na kerney) par malamat farmata hai. tumhen chahiye ke danai (maamlat mein soojh bojh, mehnat aur koshish) se kaam lo, phir jab koi maamla tum par ghalib aa jaey to kaho (حسبي الله ونعم الوكيل)."
3628,Hazrat Amr bin Shareed apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maaldaar ka qarz ki adaegi mein taal matol se kaam lena uski be-Izzati aur saza ko halal kar deta hai. ibne Mubarak ne kaha : uski be-Izzatii ko halal kar deta hai. yani uskey sath sakhti se pesh aaya jaey. aur usko saza dena halal hai. yani usey qaid kiya ja sakta hai.
3629,Harmaas bin Habib . . . eik dehati aadmi tha. . . wo apney walid se wo unke dada se riwayat karta hai ke main apney eik maqrooz ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laya to aapney mujhey farmaya : ''iskey sath chimta reh.'' phir aapney mujhey farmaya : ''aey bano Tameem ke bhai ! to apney qaidi ke sath kya karna chahta hai?''
3630,Janab Behaz bin Hakim apney walid se wo unke dada (Muawiya bin Haida Qusheiri (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko tohmat (shubha) mein qaid kiya tha.
3631,Janab Behaz bin Hakim apney walid se wo unke dada (Hazrat Muawiya bin Haida Qusheiri (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ibn Qudama ne kaha : Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka bhai ya chacha aur Mo-mil ( ibn Hisham ( ne kaha : beshak wo ( Muawiya ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke rubaru khada hua jabkey aap khutba irshad farma rahey they. usney kaha : merey hamsaayon ko kis bina par pakda gaya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se do baar munh pher liya. phir Muawiya ne kuch kaha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey hamsaayon ko riha kar do.'' Mo-mil ne apni riwayat mein '' khutba deney ka '' zikr nahin kya.
3632,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke maine khaibar janey ka irada kya to main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap ko salam pesh kya aur arz kya ke main khaibar jana chahta hun. aapney farmaya : ''jab tum merey wakeel ke paas pahuncho to us se pandarah wasq wasul kar lena. aur agar wo tum se koi alamat ( nishani ( talab karey to apna haath uskey galey par rakh dena .''
3633,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumhara kisi raastey ke baarey mein koi jhagda ho to saat haath raasta chhod do.''
3634,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum se koi bhai ijazat chahey ke tumhari deewar mein lakdi gaad ley, to usey mat roko.'' to saamein ne apni gardanen jhuka lein. Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : kya baat hai ke tum us se aeraz kerney lagey ho. mein usey tumharey kandhon par tikaaunga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye riwayat ibne-abi khalaf ki hai aur kamil hai."
3635,"sahabi Rasool Hazrat abu-Sarma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney (apney musalman bhai ko) nuqsan pahunchaya Allah uska nuqsan karey. aur jisney kisi (musalman) ko mashaqqat (aur pareshani) se do-chaar kya Allah usey mashaqqat (aur pareshani) mein daley.''"
3636,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke uskey eik Ansari ke baagh mein khajuron ke chand darkht they aur us Ansari ke sath ghar waley bhi rihaaish pazeer they. Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) apney darakhton ke liye jatey to us (Ansari) ko badi aziyat hoti aur usey uska is tarah aana jana bura lagta tha. Ansari ne Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se chaha ke ye darkht usko bech dey , magar Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne inkar kya. phir mutalba kya ke unke badley mein doosrey darkht le-ley. to bhi Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne inkar kya. phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur ye waqia bataya . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bhi us se kaha ke unhen usko farokht kar dey to usney inkar kya. phir aapney kaha ke unke badley mein doosrey darkht le-ley to bhi usney inkar kar diya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye usko hiba kar dey tujhey itna itna ajr milega .'' usko bahut targheeb di magar usney inkar kar diya. tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' to nuqsan deney wala hai.'' aur phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ansari se farmaya : '' jao aur uski khajuron ko ukhed dalo .''"
3637,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne pathreeli zameen mein se aaney waley pani ke eik naaley ke silsiley mein Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se jhagda kya jis se ye apney kheton ko sairab kartey they. Ansari ne Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : pani ko choden aur aagey aaney den. Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne inkar kya. (chaha ke pehley wo khud sairab kar lein ( to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''Zubair ! pehley tum pani ley lo phir apney hamsaaey ki taraf chhod diya karo.'' us par Ansari naraz ho gaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! chunkey ye aap ka phuphi zaad hai (is liye aapney ye faisla kya hai.) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra badal gaya. phir aapney farmaya : ''(Zubair)! khet ko pani dey. phir usey rok ley yahan tak ke khet ki munder tak chadh jaey.'' Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! main samajhta hun ke ye aayate-karima is silsiley mein nazil hui thi : ( فَلَا وَرَبِّكَ لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ . . .) '' qasam terey rab ki ! ye log us waqt tak momin nahin ho saktey jab tak ke ye apney tamam jhagdon mein aap ko apna qazi aur faisal na maan lein, phir jo faisla aap kar den uskey baarey mein unke dilon mein koi tangi bhi na aaye aur khoob khushi se tasleem kar lein.''"
3638,"Janab Solba bin abi Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney apney badon se suna tha, wo bayan kartey they ke banu Qureza main eik Quraishi ka zameen ka eik tukda tha. wadi mahzor mein un logon ka pani ke silsiley mein jhagda ho gaya jisey wo aapas mein taqseem kya kartey they. wo ye muqadma Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaye. to aapney un mein faisla farmaya ke jab pani takhney takhney tak aa jaey to phir ooper wala usey nichey waley ki taraf janey se na rokey."
3639,Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo ( Shuaib ( apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wadi mahzor mein naaley ke pani ke silsiley mein faisla farmaya tha ke pani rok liya jaey yahan tak ke takhney takhney tak aa jaey phir ooper wala nichey waley ki janib chhod dey .
3640,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein jhagda laye . unka eik khajoor ke darkht ke ird-gird ehatey (zameen ki hudood jo us darkht ke sath lazim aur mulhiq ho sakti hai) ke baarey mein jhagda tha. to aapney hukm diya ke us darkht ka ( tool ( naapa jaey. usey naapa gaya to wo saat haath hua. dusri hadees mein hai ke wo paanch haath hua. to aapney uska faisla farma diya. raawi hadees Abdul-Azeez bin Muhammad ne kaha : pas aapney us darkht ki eik chhadi ke baarey mein hukm diya, usi se usey naapa gaya."
